---

export interface Props {
	title?: string;
  subtitle? : string;
  tagline? : string;

}

const {
	title = await Astro.slots.render('title'),
  subtitle = await Astro.slots.render('subtitle'),
  tagline = await Astro.slots.render('tagline'),
} = Astro.props;
---

<section class="w-screen h-fit flex flex-col justify-around items-center" id="about">
    <div class="w-full h-1/4 p-5 text-center">
        {
        tagline && (
            <p
              class="text-base text-red-400 dark:text-red-400 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase"
              set:html={tagline}
            />
          )
        }
        {
            title && (
              <h1
                class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading dark:text-gray-200"
                set:html={title}
              />
            )
        }
        {subtitle && <p class="text-xl text-muted mb-6 dark:text-white/75" set:html={subtitle} />}
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-4/6 hidden sm:grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 m-10 pl-12 place-items-stretch">
      <div class="flex flex-col dark:text-white">
        <div class="text-3xl">
          Fast, responsive websites.
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg opacity-75">
          Got a dream? I can help you put it online.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col dark:text-white">
        <div class="text-3xl">
          Python Development
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg opacity-75">
          It can be used for eveything, so lets use it for something!
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col dark:text-white">
        <div class="text-3xl">
          Game Development
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg opacity-75">
          Wanna make a game? My experience with Unity and PyGame makes me a flexible choice for your next project.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col dark:text-white">
        <div class="text-3xl">
          3D Modelling
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg opacity-75">
          Need game assets? Want to bring your story to life with a custom animation? I work with Blender and SolidWorks to model things digitally. 
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col dark:text-white">
        <div class="text-3xl">
          Penetration Testing
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg opacity-75">
          Is your server secure? Need a Trojan in a pinch? 
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col dark:text-white">
        <div class="text-3xl">
          General Programming
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg opacity-75">
          C#, C, Java, JavaScript, Python, Bash, DuckyScript. 
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sm:hidden w-screen grid grid-col-2 place-items-left">

    </div>
    <div class="sm:hidden w-screen grid grid-col-1 gap-5 place-items-center">
      <div class="card card-side w-5/6 pl-5 bg-base-100">
        <figure>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-world-www" width="8em" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M19.5 7a9 9 0 0 0 -7.5 -4a8.991 8.991 0 0 0 -7.484 4" /><path d="M11.5 3a16.989 16.989 0 0 0 -1.826 4" /><path d="M12.5 3a16.989 16.989 0 0 1 1.828 4" /><path d="M19.5 17a9 9 0 0 1 -7.5 4a8.991 8.991 0 0 1 -7.484 -4" /><path d="M11.5 21a16.989 16.989 0 0 1 -1.826 -4" /><path d="M12.5 21a16.989 16.989 0 0 0 1.828 -4" /><path d="M2 10l1 4l1.5 -4l1.5 4l1 -4" /><path d="M17 10l1 4l1.5 -4l1.5 4l1 -4" /><path d="M9.5 10l1 4l1.5 -4l1.5 4l1 -4" /></svg>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">        
          <span>
            <h2 class="card-title">
              Fast, responsive websites.
            </h2>
          </span>
          <p>Got a dream? I can help you put it online. I specialize in React, specifically the Astro Framework. My websites have high SEO scores, and are made with accesibility in mind. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-side w-5/6 pl-5 bg-base-100">
        <figure>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-python" width="8em" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 9h-7a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h3" /><path d="M12 15h7a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-4a2 2 0 0 0 -2 -2h-3" /><path d="M8 9v-4a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-4a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v5a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-4" /><path d="M11 6l0 .01" /><path d="M13 18l0 .01" /></svg>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Python Development</h2>
          <p>It can be used for eveything, so lets use it for something. File management, task automation, data analysis. Automate everything!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-side w-5/6 pl-5 bg-base-100">
        <figure>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-unity" width="3em" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M14 3l6 4v7" /><path d="M18 17l-6 4l-6 -4" /><path d="M4 14v-7l6 -4" /><path d="M4 7l8 5v9" /><path d="M20 7l-8 5" /></svg>
        </figure> 
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Game Development</h2>
          <p>Wanna make a game? My experience with Unity and PyGame makes me a flexible choice for your next project. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-side w-5/6 pl-5 bg-base-100">
        <figure>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-blender" width="3em" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M15 14m-6 0a6 5 0 1 0 12 0a6 5 0 1 0 -12 0" /><path d="M15 14m-1 0a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0" /><path d="M3 16l9 -6.5" /><path d="M6 9h9" /><path d="M13 5l5.65 5" /></svg>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">3D Modelling</h2>
          <p>Need game assets? Want to bring your story to life with a custom animation?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-side w-5/6 pl-5 bg-base-100">
        <figure>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-lock" width="3em" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M5 13a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-6z" /><path d="M11 16a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 0 0 -2 0" /><path d="M8 11v-4a4 4 0 1 1 8 0v4" /></svg>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Penetration Testing </h2>
          <p>Is your server secure? Need a Trojan in a pinch? </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-side w-5/6 pl-5 bg-base-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">General Programming</h2>
          <p>C#, C, Java, JavaScript, Python, Bash, DuckyScript. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>


